{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e8f405f6f1","title":"对江青还陷周恩来的批评","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1400fe3f19","index":0,"year":1973,"month":12,"day":9,"articleId":"e8f405f6f1"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"6bd33a1bd2","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"e8f405f6f1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周恩来。"},{"id":"5e7819e5c3","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"e8f405f6f1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指江青。"}],"contents":[{"id":"afa23fca02","type":"title","text":"对江青远陷周恩来的批评！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"e8f405f6f1"},{"id":"6bd33a1bd2","type":"paragraph","text":"这这次会开得好，很好，就是有人讲错了两句话。一个是讲十一次路线斗争，不应该那么讲，实际上也不是。对总理可以批评，林彪就不行。一个是讲总理追不及待。他不是追不及待，她自己可才是道不及待。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"e8f405f6f1"},{"id":"5e7819e5c3","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]1973年11月，在政治局批错误的会议上，江青提出这是第十一次路线斗争，姚文元也跟着这样说。江青还指贵周总理是追不及待地要代替主席。12月9日，毛泽东在会见尼泊尔国王后，曾分三批先后同周恩来、王洪文和唐闻生、王海容两人谈了话。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"e8f405f6f1"}],"page":{"id":"ea050dc28a","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"e8f405f6f1","start":451,"end":451}}}},"__N_SSG":true}